                    </p>
					<p>
						Furthermore there is an interesting book about shortest paths: <a hre=
f=3D"http://www-m9.ma.tum.de/Ruth/WebHome">Das Geheimnis des k=C3=BCrzesten=
 Weges</a>
					</p>
					<p>
						<a href=3D"http://www.ma.tum.de/Studium/StudieninteressierteEn">Study=
ing mathematics at the TU M=C3=BCnchen</a> answers all questions about grap=
h theory (if an answer is known).
					</p>
                </div>
